<HL>
   Treasury Plans to Sell
   $16.4 Billion of Bills
</HL>
<DATE>
04/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C19
</SO>
<IN>
FINANCIAL, INTEREST RATES, LEASING (FIN)
BOND MARKET NEWS (BON)
</IN>
