   Who's News:
   Prudential-Bache Hires
   Brophy to Head Desk
   For Institution Trades
</HL>
<DATE>
04/04/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   WNEWS
