Acceptance Corp.: 8.275% 30 to 44 days; 8.25% 45 to 59 days;
8.20% 60 to 89 days; 8.15% 90 to 119 days; 8.10% 120 to 149
days; 8.05% 150 to 179 days; 8% 180 to 270 days.
                                                                                                       

